In Actian 4GL, it is not possible to add a single user to multiple groups at once by using the alter group statement. You would have to use the alter group statement for each group individually. For example:
```sql
alter group sales_clerks add users (johnm);
alter group marketing_team add users (johnm);
```

```sql
alter group tel_sales drop users (harryk, joanb);
```
